    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels so heavy though. like i'm dragging this empty version of myself around every single day and it's exhausting. i look at people my age and they seem so... present. i just feel like a hollowed out remain. like there's nothing left of the person i was supposed to be.",
